"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:24:02.000Z","msg":"自從中資宣布收購香港m記之後，我已經無再食<br />\n<br />\n之前仲見到有人玩屯貨，係咁買m記出嘅咩和風紫菜粉，幾箱咁買<br />\n話唔鍾意中資，但又仆曬咁去買中資公司啲產品，你可以見到啲人幾有骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，某程度上同支那人抵制日貨無分別"},{"pid":"6f54c8a2a958eab516c3baddb130c65304b8a942","tid":513720,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f961b27e135adbb5ed3156dbcff65f937796f26","tid":513720,"uid":25635,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T00:02:19.000Z","msg":"無錢啊屌，唔食m記可以食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:33:15.000Z","msg":"KFC 狗飯，吉嘢家下午茶，一樣廿鳩幾蚊"},{"pid":"8394a49a0b99c3da1fa1bd1d806b001bdb94c354","tid":513720,"uid":24368,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日本仔都做到點解我地唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多年黎就係因為唔團結呢個地方先衰到咁<br />\n今次就踏出第一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊罷食支那m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解？</blockquote>有好多原因<br />\n福喜<br />\n加價<br />\n板雞<br />\n全翼</blockquote><br />\n你會唔會牽強左少少<br />\n你舉既例子得福喜事件先係罷食既原因<br />\n<br />\n加價？你有冇諗過成本？減你人工得唔得？<br />\n佢都仲有三個24蚊餐，定時有優惠，都過得去啦。<br />\n<br />\n板雞？人地想出咩餐就咩餐架啦，點解你要take it for granted？間舖又唔係你開，點解要下下就哂你口味？其他食肆落架左某啲食品你又要抗議？根本唔係所有野都永遠不變。<br />\n<br />\n講埋全翼，根本人地個餐就set好兩鎚兩翼，人地之前俾你叫全翼其實只係額外，根本就唔係理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n我只係理性討論，唔係話幫佢"},{"pid":"721ca1b87f0c4511c7b7d362e7540f311b230901","tid":513720,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9875d084a68d41e52d94df1ad9f432a5bcc557","tid":513720,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0941832e786620569af1e45ee306c61edc157d99","tid":513720,"uid":131441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22c09ea39c7a652e5e32c90ae71b2c5a9ca69527","tid":513720,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"唔好講咁多，對抗霸權。平賣你層樓，抗地產"},{"pid":"25dcfbcd18d291bb3966d7f6d9af4c0eac4a0b4c","tid":513720,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:09:27.000Z","msg":"食緊bigmac睇呢個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca93983b62650535e9cdfcadfd49904be9930879","tid":513720,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"461c296535d7bb08873ab4273a1c4e4c741e77e8","tid":513720,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4ad7334363482e8f03d1350f6776c129d2ba05","tid":513720,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ba678e13a1a503dad84fe4baee219bc8bc860d","tid":513720,"uid":41922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:22:54.000Z","msg":"日本多返人食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出左事之後仲加人工添"},{"pid":"cf3473df40d08918e4cc2b17fa1f682326420c69","tid":513720,"uid":53196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"睇到呢個po先發覺已經冇食6年"},{"pid":"584af0860ec9887071baaefb18db4da95a46955e","tid":513720,"uid":104213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:28:26.00